tps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F003103_09686b7d7911f62bbd01d290ac576c0e.jpg&h=ddec6b8d&s={SIZE}\" />佢呢間話有貸切風呂係咪即係私人風呂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係</blockquote><br />\n貸切風呂係公用既<br />\n如果間房寫帶露天浴池就係有，否則就唔肯定(可以係溫泉亦可以係普通浴缸)<br />\n不過就算係帶露天浴池，都有分出溫泉水定熱水<br />\n所以酒店網其實唔岩你用，俾D時間研究下日文版樂天/Jalan啦，唔識訂都可以用黎搵名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d2d4ed2b25838328e2105026049aa05d1aac13","tid":412340,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住過箱根有間3000幾都唔錯，有個鐵缸喺露台，然後出温泉水</blockquote><br />\n我去札幌有冇平靚正嘅私湯介紹？</blockquote><br />\n札幌邊會有溫泉，有無第二個地點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5c8006a65a5a5a974f934ad8ae63b31c53370e","tid":412340,"uid":49797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"不如你貼條link出黎俾人幫你睇<br />\n我知你係唔識<br />\n但你d對答真係幾9唔搭8咁好難幫你"},{"pid":"066244d03bebbbb769bac76386c112eedec308f9","tid":412340,"uid":49797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://同埋建議你上booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8Abooking.com&d=XSbuDkYM8s2eWeda%2FQGdIMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=decd69f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">同埋建議你上booking.com</a>睇左先<br />\nbooking d資訊最user friendly<br />\n睇岩先再格價"},{"pid":"dd23ffe0c6c0dcee82554c9c2bd355fe2268e6cd","tid":412340,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你貼條link出黎俾人幫你睇<br />\n我知你係唔識<br />\n但你d對答真係幾9唔搭8咁好難幫你</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.rakuten.com.hk/hotel/Japan-Hokkaido-Sapporo-Jyozankei_Onsen_Jyozankei_D